{"tid":190690,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★炒燶iPhone冒簽提款20萬填氹　滙豐職員候判","createTime":"2017-04-07T09:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T09:06:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"842ec40ab5ed6dc0bf17ade44436ff1aec075f37","tid":190690,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:34:52.000Z","msg":"4月 7日(五) 13:20<br />\n炒燶iPhone冒簽提款20萬填氹　滙豐職員候判<br />\n<br />\n一名滙豐銀行女職員，承認冒客戶簽名擅自提走20萬港元。(資料圖片)<br />\n31歲滙豐銀行女櫃位職員葉芷妮，因「炒燶」iPhone遭內地生意拍檔追數，對方更要挾要親身到銀行追討，葉聲稱怕上級知道她欠債會丟失工作，竟冒客戶簽名擅自從對方戶口提走20萬港元，銀行翌日揭發問題轉帳，報警處理並將葉解僱。<br />\n<br />\n被告葉芷妮今日在東區法院承認一項使用偽造文件罪，裁判官將案件押後至本月21日，等候其背景報告後判刑，期間被告須還押看管，而裁判官明言會判處監禁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170407/bkn-20170407132043486-0407_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170407%2Fbkn-20170407132043486-0407_00822_001.html&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=59c29065\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170407/bkn-20170407132043486-0407_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"da161969568bcb4827d935b47e6c9e459ce69bbd","tid":190690,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bdbc3dfb940568ff4850b83548b0496cd72bff","tid":190690,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"炒iPhone<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"